<input  type="checkbox" 
        id="autoSubmitResourceId"
        name="autoSubmitResourceId"
        [ngModel]="isEnabled"
        (ngModelChange)="testFx()"
        (change)="change()"
        #ctrl="ngModel"
>

<label  for="autoSubmitResourceId" 
        id="autoSubmitResourceIdLabel">
        
    Odpáliť automaticky po vložení
    
</label>
